lead_paragraph: Ryan Lochte powered out to a big lead in the event he won four years ago at the London Olympics, his powerful arms churning through the water, looking very much like a lock for another trip to the games.

headline.main: Stunner at US Olympic Swim Trials: Lochte Beaten in 400 IM
